	  Follow make's normal precedence rules.

	* gendirdeps.mk: allow customization of the header.
	  eg. for FreeBSD:
	  GENDIRDEPS_HEADER= echo '\# ${FreeBSD:L:@v@$$$v$$ @:M*F*}';

